query:
SELECT 
  s.id,
  s.token,
  s.gestanteId,
  s.expiraEm,
  s.createdAt,
  g.nome,
  g.email,
  CASE 
    WHEN s.expiraEm > NOW() THEN 'VÁLIDA'
    ELSE 'EXPIRADA'
  END as status_sessao
FROM sessoesGestante s
JOIN gestantes g ON s.gestanteId = g.id
WHERE s.token = '4889f65eb446b1476d08472ac2bde173e65e4c035c25f12cece37becca1f932a993f2a8b57199dd123ec716329d1bf63f8e02ed1d0e9b7e201967ed8accd691a'
LIMIT 1;
